# Cross-origin isolation is required for Whisper.cpp (SharedArrayBuffer / pthread).
# src/server.ts already sets these on SSR responses, but this file guarantees the
# same headers on any statically-served response (offline.html, precached assets,
# Cloudflare Pages fallback paths) so `crossOriginIsolated === true` everywhere.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: credentialless
